name: ViewDisplaySettings
shortdesc: Options for display performance settings, which influence the speed and quality with which an object draws and redraws.

property.name: HIGH_QUALITY
property.shortdesc: Slower performance; displays high-resolution graphics and high-quality transparencies and turns on anti-aliasing.

property.name: TYPICAL
property.shortdesc: Moderate performance speed; displays proxy graphics and low-quality transparencies and turns on anti-aliasing.

property.name: OPTIMIZED
property.shortdesc: Best performance; grays out graphics and turns off transparency and anti-aliasing.
